{"tid":1417361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽後檢討]荃灣罷工運動","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:07:21.000Z","uid":265234,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b957b71d1d08e0328f553f1af39f47e942ad762","tid":1417361,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"今日留左係荃灣，開post係想大家檢討下有咩下次可以做好D，日後其他地區行動都可以參考下，唔係想怪責任何人/事，歡迎大家討論下俾下意見。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>好：</strong></span><br />\n- 荃灣今日行動機動性強，一收到風就迅速轉場，避免正面硬碰。<br />\n- 多個天橋/商場位置附近行動，有利觀察形勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>改善：</strong></span><br />\n- 一開始時行動散亂，係唔同地方設左好多路障，結果變左迷宮陣，令D車好難搵路走。<br />\n- 路障覆蓋太廣，但設完唔係諗住留守，影響區內居民(不少地方需靠邨巴,小巴接駁市中心,交通入唔到去)，但居民見唔到有抗爭(因為好多位都無哂人)，只係見到周圍留低既影響，建議應集中一兩個主要據點或以直線發展設陣。<br />\n- 目標不夠明確而且分散，戰線太多太散(配以人數考慮)，有荃灣西楊屋道沙咀道一帶，有荃灣警署（愉景新城），有新界南總區（大窩口），甚至仲想過埋葵芳。我明白目標係想打游擊，但理想應係一齊撤退然後坐車轉場，好過一堆步兵走來走去。<br />\n<br />\n利申:行動初哥,戰術經驗不多,但希望顧及民意,因為民意是整場運動的基礎"},{"pid":"68f59f4b2c8ee4b51ba6625de9a4fa97d5a89594","tid":1417361,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XPMFdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XPMFdo.png&h=c46df892&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEJE0do.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEJE0do.png&h=e162505a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003117_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003117_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=6d0223dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003118_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003118_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=ee304f66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003119_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003119_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png&h=5539c162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f1266cad87fae4a44fab54cd0ef6321350e92c7","tid":1417361,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"尋晚襯記得出左先，但實在太多事發生，而家再推返"}]}